text:
Ananyaaaaaaaa!
I wish I could turn back time and meet you sooner. That way, I could spend a little more time with you. I can't even imagine how I would've survived MSE and college without you. I still remember your smile when I told you about my branch change, and I literally knew that I will be able to go through it. From sharing the same department to sharing life secrets, we've come a long way, and I couldn't be more thankful to have this cute-chubby-witty-sassy person in my life. Classes k baad ki chai, labs ki masti, lab assignments ka rona, tera raat ko 2 bje aake Maggie ki demand krna aur mere room ki tareef will be missed a lot :(
Thank you for always being you. Thank you for always being there to listen to me. Life wouldn't have been the same without you. I guess I'll cry my eyes out If I write anymore. 
Hope I meet you real soon and cook amazingly delicious maggie for you( is baar kettle wali nhi hogi :P). Stay safe and take care. And just remember that I'm just one call away. 
Love you <3 <3
PS: Congrats!! XD

Mohtarama!
First year m Yashika ki room m gyi thi to tujhse pahli baar mili thi. Fir ek tatti aurat ki badaulat kaafi baat hone lg gyi thi apni aur ab vo situation aa chuki h ki baatein khatm hi nhi hotiğŸ˜‚ (as much as I hate to say this, ye chutiya ladki ne bahut acche dost diye hain mujhe ğŸ˜…)
Mujhe bhi nhi pta kyu pr teri har baat maan hi jaati hu m end m ( especially khaane k maamle mğŸ˜†). Ye chicken premiyon k beech m tu iklauti insaan h jo mere sahara bani hğŸ˜‚(white sauce pasta is lubâ¤ï¸). 
Aur bhai sach m, dar lgta h yr tujhse. Tune kabhi kuch nhi bola fir bhi lgta h yaar ğŸ˜‚. 
Vo din bda maja aaya tha yr jb tu high hui thi. Mtlb doosron ki jin harkaton se tumhe ulti ho jaaye, vo saari harkatein kri tumne us. Badi cute lg rhi thi yr tuğŸ˜†. Aise hi high hote rhna.
Meri Maggie ka sabse jyada faayda uthaya h tune vaiseğŸ˜›
Aur bahut chaap liya yr, humein bhi sikha do thoda. Drams m tum, dance m tum, sports m tum, photography m tum, FMC m tum, techkriti m tum, antragni m tum, udghosh m tum....har jagh chhayi hui ho dostğŸ™
I'm glad ki college k last 2 mahine tere saath beete. Agar us din tu U turn le leti Jaipur se to bahut kuch miss ho jaata :P. Bahut maja vaise un dino m....tere saare hidden talents the vo pta lag gye hme bhi. 
Yahan tareef krke kya krna, pta to tujhe h hi sb. Bas aise hi khaati peeti aur chaapti rah. Baaki sb baatein krne k liye to milte rahenge apan. Treats bhi leni hain tujhse abhi to.
Aur kanjoosi km kar do thodi, ab to kamane lg gyi ho.
Aur haan, bahut samajhdar h tu, bro! Tumhare jaise samajhdar doston ki bahut jarurat h zindagi m. Shukriya is dosti k liye.
Hope I'll see you soon. Take care!

text:
Hello Madam! 
It's actually been 5 years! I vividly remember the day I met you in Dakshana, and I still can't believe that our fantasy of going to the same college came true. I was so happy ( even more shocked) when I saw you in front of the hall office on my first day at IITK. It's been one hell of a ride, and you've always been my saviour throughout. And yes, our random 2 AM conversations about literally everything, including friends, food, fashion, crushes, have made it so much more tolerable and entertaining. Ice cream and Meggie sessions were icing on the cake XD ( I'll always miss this). 
You have my heart for being the most dramatic and self-obsessed ( in a good way) BFF I could ever have. And yeah, I'll keep advising you on your relationship issues ( you know kitni pro hu m isme LOL) 
Thanks a lot for making me grow so much as a person and as a friend during these 5 years. I'm going to brag about having this " Smart-Gorgeous-Badass Bestie" for the rest of my life XD. Ig itni tareef kaafi h, Baaki tareef milegi tb karungi.
Let's always be there for each other. Aur Haan, Love you <3
PS: Don't roast me for writing those cheesy lines; you made me do this :P
